videos.description: In the first half, Valparaiso's Shane Hammink puts up a nice lob to Darien Walker who finishes with the two-handed slam but then just seconds later Texas Southern answers with a dunk of their own, Derrick Griffin passes it up to Chris Thomas for the jam.
videos.headline: Valpo, Texas Southern trade alley-oops

videos.description: Homer Drew in attendance to watch his son, Bryce, coach the current Valparaiso team. Homer coached Bryce on Valpo's memorable Sweet 16 run in 1998.
videos.headline: Blast from the past with Bryce and Homer Drew.
Vashil Fernandez block leads to a Darien Walker layup.
Alec Peters steals it and makes the athletic layup.
